feat.val: This is the LMF version of an Apertium bilingual lexicon. The lexicon was automatically generated from an Apertium bilingual lexicon. In LMF, bilingual relations are expressed as relations between 'senses'. However Apertium bilingual lexicons do not include 'senses' and bilingual relations are relations between lemmas. As a consequence, each lemma is assigned one and only one sense which serves as a place holder for bilingual relations.
do jeito que veio ao mundo
com uma mão na frente e outra atrás
com tudo que eu tenho direito
cria fama e deita na cama
amb una mà davant i una mà darrere
amb totes les de la llei
a la curta o a la llarga
com sa mare el va dur al món
amb un peu a l'altre barri
al cap i a la fi
fes te fama i fot te a jeure
amb una mà al davant i una mà al darrere
com qui no vol la cosa
